NOTICE / 声明

This project, "gutachten-criminal-case" (鉴定式刑法案例研习 Skill), is an
original work by 游初 (Youchu).

本项目"gutachten-criminal-case"（鉴定式刑法案例研习 Skill）由游初原创开发。

The skill implements the Gutachtenstil (鉴定式案例分析法) methodology
for Chinese criminal law practice. It builds on a tripartite crime
theory system (Dreistufiger Deliktsaufbau) and features an internal
offense-examination-engine that performs independent legal analysis without
external knowledge base dependencies. On all major doctrinal controversies,
the skill takes a doctrine-neutral stance: it provides a user-configurable
school-of-thought switch (see workflow/0-cold-start-interview.md §1.5) so
that practitioners may freely select the position they find most reasonable
on each contested issue. When the user makes no selection, the skill
defaults to the dualistic Handlungsunwert position (Position A).

本技能将鉴定式案例分析方法论（Gutachtenstil）适配中国刑法实务，
以三阶层犯罪论体系（Dreistufiger Deliktsaufbau）为基底，通过内置罪名检视
引擎（offense-examination-engine）独立完成法律分析，无需依赖外部知识库。
在所有重大学派分歧议题上，本技能采"不预设权威学说"的中立立场：
通过 workflow/0-cold-start-interview.md §1.5 提供学派开关，让用户在每一
争议议题上自由选择其认为合理的立场。用户未选择时，默认采"行为无价值
二元论"（立场 A）。

